      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TURBO TATE (7) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (27.96) at this track behind Clifton Kuna in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can go on with it. SUNSET PARIS (8) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (28.25) in a Grade 5/6 at this track. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Has the ability to give this a shake. SON OF MANADO (1) collided with another runner last time and always well back when fifth (23.20) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Has the ability and can measure up. SMELL LIKE ROSE (4) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
